# FLL — First Line Logistics Platform Context

## Quick Summary
Saudi delivery logistics company (فيرست لاين لوجستيكس). Multi-portal web platform managing couriers, orders, complaints, finance, fleet, and HR across 7 delivery platforms (HungerStation, Keeta, Ninja, Mrsool, ToYou, Jahez, Careem).

