## Hosting & Deployment

| Layer | Service | Details |
|-------|---------|---------|
| **Frontend** | Vercel | Static files, auto-deploy from GitHub on push to `main` |
| **Domain** | fll.sa + www.fll.sa | Managed by Vercel |
| **Git** | github.com/mshari-11/firstlinelog.com | Public repo |
| **Backend API** | AWS API Gateway | `https://xr7wsfym5k.execute-api.me-south-1.amazonaws.com` |
| **Auth** | AWS Cognito | Pool: `me-south-1_aJtmQ0QrN`, Client: `3mva1s8p68h8djl04n6vs41gkb` |
| **Database 1** | Supabase PostgreSQL | URL: `djebhztfewjfyyoortvv.supabase.co`, 98 tables |
| **Database 2** | AWS DynamoDB | 38+ tables (complaints, tasks, audit, payouts, etc.) |
| **Lambda** | AWS Lambda | `fll-platform-api-prod` (Node.js 20) |
| **Region** | me-south-1 (Bahrain) | All AWS resources |
| **Email** | AWS SES | Domain: fll.sa, verified |
| **Storage** | AWS S3 | 8 buckets (KYC, finance, exports, ops-raw, etc.) |
| **AI** | AWS Bedrock | Claude Haiku, me-south-1 |
| **Events** | AWS EventBridge | SLA scanner (hourly), daily backup (2AM) |

