## Design System (v6)

| Element | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Theme** | Dark glassmorphism |
| **Font** | IBM Plex Sans Arabic (300-700) |
| **Icons** | Lucide (CDN: unpkg.com/lucide@latest) |
| **Charts** | Chart.js 4.x (dark defaults) |
| **Background** | `#0e1a2e` with radial gradient overlays |
| **Cards** | `rgba(21,34,56,0.7)` + `backdrop-filter:blur(10px)` |
| **Border** | `rgba(56,189,248,0.1)` |
| **Text** | `#e2e8f0` (primary), `#94a3b8` (muted) |
| **Accent** | `#38bdf8` (blue), `#fbbf24` (gold), `#22c55e` (green) |
| **Buttons** | `linear-gradient(135deg, #0284c7, #7c3aed)` |
| **Badges** | Semi-transparent: `rgba(color, 0.15)` with light text |
| **Stat Cards** | Gradient top border (3px), hover lift effect |

