## Auth Flow

1. User visits `/unified-login` (rewrites to `/` → Skywork bundle)
2. `fll-login-fixer.js` intercepts login form
3. POST `/auth/login` → Cognito
4. If MFA → shows OTP page → POST `/auth/respond-mfa`
5. On success → saves `fll_user` + `fll_token` to localStorage
6. Redirects based on Cognito group:
   - `admin` → `/admin-dashboard`
   - `finance` → `/staff-finance`
   - `hr` → `/staff-hr`
   - `ops` → `/staff-ops`
   - `fleet` → `/staff-fleet`
   - `driver` → `/courier-dashboard`

### Cognito Groups
`admin`, `finance`, `hr`, `ops`, `fleet`, `driver`, `manager`, `supervisor`, `viewer`

