## Supabase Tables (Key Tables)

### Core
- `couriers` — Driver profiles (name, NID, phone, STC bank, city, contract_type, status)
- `orders` — Delivery orders (courier_id, platform, order_date, gross_earnings, deductions, net_earnings)
- `staff_users` — Staff profiles
- `departments` — Company departments
- `complaints` — Supabase-side complaints

### Finance (schema: finance)
- `fin_platforms` — 7 platforms config
- `fin_cities` — 16 Saudi cities
- `fin_platform_rate_cards` — Commission rates
- `fin_platform_bonus_rules` — Bonus rules
- `fin_platform_penalty_rules` — Penalty rules
- `driver_wallets` — Wallet balances
- `driver_wallet_ledger` — Immutable transaction log
- `payout_batches` — Batch payouts
- `reconciliation_batches` — Reconciliation runs
- `manual_adjustments` — Manual corrections
- `fraud_rules` — Fraud detection rules
- `fraud_flags` — Fraud alerts

### Fleet
- `fll_vehicles` — Vehicle records
- `fll_fuel_log` — Fuel tracking
- `fll_accidents` — Accident records

### HR
- `driver_training_records` — Training
- `driver_ratings` — Performance ratings
- `benefits` — Employee benefits

### System
- `audit_log` — Audit trail
- `chat_history` — AI chat logs
- `email_templates` — Email templates
- `kyc_files` — KYC documents

