## Current Portal Features

### Admin Dashboard (18 sections)
Overview, Couriers, Orders, Complaints, Platforms, Finance, Staff, Departments, Tasks, Notifications, Audit Log, Approvals, Integrations, AI, Settings, Fraud Detection, Upload Center, Daily Finance Close

### Staff Finance (12 tabs)
Payouts, Earnings, Invoices, Platform Statements, Bank Transfers, Monthly Reports, Charts, Upload Center, Wallets, Reconciliation, AI Insights, Profitability

### Staff HR (6 tabs)
Staff, Attendance, Leave, Recruitment, Training, Performance

### Staff Ops (6 tabs)
Overview, Assignments, Schedule, Complaints, Performance, Reports

### Staff Fleet (4 tabs)
Vehicles, Fuel, Maintenance, Accidents

### Staff Dashboard (5 tabs)
Overview, Tasks, Requests, Notifications, Profile

### Courier Dashboard (5 tabs)
Overview, Earnings, Deliveries, Profile/KYC, Support

