## Critical Rules for Development

1. **NEVER modify** `index.html` or `assets/` — Skywork static bundle
2. **ALL changes are ADDITIVE** — never delete working code
3. **Dark theme mandatory** — use CSS variables above
4. **Arabic RTL** — all pages are `dir="rtl"` `lang="ar"`
5. **IBM Plex Sans Arabic** — only font allowed
6. **Lucide Icons** — CDN, use `data-lucide` attributes, call `lucide.createIcons()` after DOM updates
7. **Supabase** for structured data (couriers, orders, finance)
8. **DynamoDB** for operational data (complaints, tasks, audit, approvals)
9. **Push to `main`** → auto-deploys to fll.sa via Vercel
10. **Region: me-south-1** (Bahrain) for all AWS resources

